 Berserk is such a story, an Epic.\
~Story~ 10/10\
In a reflection to the medieval crusades spanning from 1095 – 1291CE we can get a good understand of the time period of Berserk. If we can't pin out a time period\
          \
        that reflects our own it's hard to relate to the story itself. Berserk takes this reflection in two different ways. The Crusades and/or The 100 Years War.\
