    [33] = {
      firstname = "Isma",
      description = "Isma is a young fishing girl who lives by the outskirts of the village on an island that holds the Sea God. \
 Isma has short hair with long bangs that will cover half her face at times. Her eyes are much rounder that that of and average person and has a few frekkals on her nose.\
 \
 She claims that her father was courting a merrow but admits that she is all human, dispite this she can still fish as good as any other merrow and Schierke saw a strange aquatic od/ aura around her. It was because of this and the story of the merrow sealing the Sea God on the island that she now lives on, the people of the village shun her and so she decided to move to the outskirts of town.\
 \
 She later realizes she can turn into a merrow (mermaid) when she dives in the water to save Isidro who fell over board.\
 She also decides to join Guts' group.\
\
