    [48] = {
      firstname = "Nina",
      description = "A young, reckless prostitute. Nina is a member of Luca's group of travelling prostitutes. During her time at Albion, she dated Joachim, a young refugee. At one time she was a member of a heretic cult group, who held orgies in a cave, worshipping the Goddess of Fire. During her ordeal in the cave, Nina contracted a disease similar to tuberculosis. \
 Soon after the Tower of Conviction was destroyed, she apologised to Luca for all the trouble she had caused, but soon left afterwards with Joachim, who survived the fall from the cliffs.\
